message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely sub-category as the paper deals with signal processing and machine learning techniques applied to music audio. Other likely sub-categories could be cs.SI (due to the use of neural networks), cs.SD.LG (due to the use of a large dataset), cs.SD.MA (due to the use of music analysis techniques), and cs.SD.CS (due to the use of convolutional neural networks).
